16
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:55,000
Buti na lang at pinapasok ni Mr. Shen
nangungunang espesyalista sa bansa

17
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,060
mula sa City A kahapon,

18
00:01:57,460 --> 00:02:00,380
kaya ang operasyon ay maaaring
maisagawa sa oras at epektibo.

19
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:02,060
Salamat sa iyong pagsusumikap.

20
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:02,859
salamat po.

21
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:04,019
Huwag mong hayaan na ingatan ka namin.

22
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:04,740
salamat po.

23
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,460
salamat po.

24
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:07,940
Huwag mong banggitin.

25
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:10,340
Sobrang effort mo
para sa tatay ko.

26
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:13,100
Naghahanap ka ba ng paraan
para mapalapit sa pamilya Xu?

27
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,500
Tiyo Zhaohui,

28
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:16,340
iniligtas niya si Lolo.

29
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,619
Bigla siyang naging

30
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,499
ang pinakamalaking shareholder ng Junlin Group.

31
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,459
Sino ang magsasabi

32
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:23,139
hindi siya magtatakda ng kanyang mga tingin

33
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:25,940
sa mga asset ng aming pamilya sa susunod?

34
00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:27,219
Wanxin,

35
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,979
Maganda ang assessment ko sa mga tao.

36
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:29,939
Dapat mong

37
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:30,979
lumayo ka sa kanya.

38
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:33,220
Since Mr. Xu's stable ngayon,

39
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:34,940
Hindi na kita iistorbohin pa.

40
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,260
Tingnan ang iyong sarili.

41
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:38,060
Ilalabas ko siya.

42
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:39,379
Wanxin.

43
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:39,779
Wanxin.

44
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,419
Tiyo Zhaohui.

45
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,459
(Ikatlong Palapag, Operating Room)

46
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:43,220
Dapat manatili ka
at hintayin si Lolo.

47
00:02:50,191 --> 00:02:51,420
Mr. Shen.

48
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,500
I'm sorry about that.

49
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:56,980
Humihingi ako ng tawad sa aking tiyuhin.

50
00:02:58,340 --> 00:03:00,020
Hindi mo kailangang humingi ng tawad sa sinuman.

51
00:03:02,076 --> 00:03:03,140
Wanxin.

52
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:07,899
May isang insidente

53
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,740
habang ang katawan ng iyong ama
ay dinadala pabalik sa Gang City.

54
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:13,099
Tumulong si Mr. Shen na ayusin ang lahat.

55
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:15,300
Inilagay na ang katawan
sa punerarya.

56
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:19,300
Mayroon ding ilang mga dokumento dito

57
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,940
na kailangan mong pirmahan.

58
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:27,280
(Gang City Public Mortuary,
Kagawaran ng Kalusugan)

59
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:34,440
(Gang City Public Mortuary,
Kagawaran ng Kalusugan)

60
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:52,320
